Patrick Byrne, PresidentAnthony Byrne, Vice President Susan Byrne, ComptrollerLarry Erny, Project ManagerMike Blizniak, Project ManagerDiane Vitali, Office Manager




Our Services

New ConstructionReplacement & Retrofit RoofsSlate, Tile, Wood & Asphalt ShinglesBuilt-up, Modified Bitumen, PVC, TPO & EPDM RoofingMetal RoofingCustom Metal FabricationsHistoric PreservationRoof MaintenanceRoof Coatings & RestorationsSkylights & Other AccessoriesRoof Vacuuming ServicesAsbestos Abatement






Our philosophy is simple. We believe in providing our customers with high quality products, excellent service and superior performance.Since our founding, Weaver Metal and Roofing has successfully installed and maintained roofing systems on major projects throughout Western New York - earning us our reputation as one of Buffalo's premier roofing and architectural sheet metal contractors. Such projects include Ford's Buffalo Stamping Plant, the University at Buffalo's South Campus, General Motors' Tonawanda Engine Plant, and many area schools. Examples of Weaver Metal and Roofing's sheet metal work adorn a number of historical landmarks including Our Lady of Victory Basilica in Lackawanna and Corpus Christi Church in Buffalo.Weaver Metal and Roofing is signatory to collective bargaining agreements with Roofers Local #74 and Sheet Metal Workers Local #71, and we are an accredited member of the Better Business Bureau.
 
 

Copyright © 2012, Weaver Metal and Roofing, Inc.  All rights reserved | 40 Appenheimer Avenue, Buffalo NY, 14214 | 716.891.8844
